un,

00:03:03.375 --> 00:03:06.541
kh'bin geven nokh a kleyn meydele. kh'bin gegan in shkole,

00:03:06.582 --> 00:03:08.736
un ikh bin geven a bisl gliklekh.

00:03:09.433 --> 00:03:11.637
host gehat shvester un bruder?

