un mayn bruder, eyner, ⟨, hot, hot,⟩ hey- hot geheysn

00:03:30.566 --> 00:03:31.685
VIKTOR,

00:03:31.928 --> 00:03:33.626
un MORDEKHAY,

00:03:33.717 --> 00:03:35.010
un Avreml

00:03:35.942 --> 00:03:36.520
'KAY.

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:39.510
⟨i⟩n vos far a hoyz hostu geven?

00:03:39.775 --> 00:03:42.958
ikh hob, kh'hob, mir hobn gehat a gute sh-, HOUSE.

00:03:43.352 --> 00:03:45.550
 mir hobn gelebt nit shlekht.

00:03:45.985 --> 00:03:48.392
mayn foter hot gearbet,

00:03:48.718 --> 00:03:50.940
un mir kinder hobn gelernt.

00:03:51.570 --> 00:03:53.892
vos far a zakhn hostu gelernt?

00:03:53.967 --> 00:03:57.454
UNK gelernt in shko- in der, in, in der shule.

00:03:57.612 --> 00:04:02.483
d⟨i⟩, s'ershte hob ikh gelernt in a HEBREW shule fir yor,

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:06.279
un kh'hob gekont shtark gut redn HEBREW, nor kh'hob fargesn.

00:04:06.606 --> 00:04:09.536
un dernokh dem hob ikh gere- gelernt in a

00:04:09.728 --> 00:04:11.747
rumenishe gimnazye

00:04:12.023 --> 00:04:13.215
tsvey yor,

00:04:13.305 --> 00:04:15.914
un nokh dem, ven s'iz gekumen tsun undz Rusland,

00:04:16.072 --> 00:04:19.053
hob ikh gelernt in a rusisher, shule

00:04:19.632 --> 00:04:21.887
eyn yor, biz der milkhome.

00:04:22.485 --> 00:04:23.072
'KAY.

00:04:23.072 --> 00:04:27.164
kenstu mir zogn fun dayn hoyz, vifl tsimer,

00:04:27.164 --> 00:04:28.503
v-...?

00:04:27.278 --> 00:04:31.862
nu, mir hobn gehat dray tsimern, groyse dray tsimern.

00:04:32.037 --> 00:04:34.360
mir hobn gehat a sheyne kikh,

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:35.709
azoy ikh gedenk,

00:04:36.019 --> 00:04:39.940
un s'iz geven a, a hoyf, a groyser hoyf,

00:04:40.542 --> 00:04:43.151
un mir hobn gehat a balkon.

00:04:44.271 --> 00:04:47.201
un, ikh veys, nisht keyn shlekhte shtub.

00:04:44.305 --> 00:04:45.041
s'iz...

00:04:47.190 --> 00:04:51.453
s'iz geven a groyse gase, lange, tsu a, a kleyne?

00:04:51.477 --> 00:04:54.241
nu, mir, kh'hob gevoynt in a kleyn shtetele;

00:04:54.241 --> 00:04:55.992
s'iz nisht geven azoy lang,

00:04:56.151 --> 00:04:58.586
vayl di sh- gantse shtot iz nisht lang,

00:04:58.586 --> 00:04:59.874
nisht geven lang.

00:04:59.540 --> 00:05:02.473
vos kenstu undz zogn v- vegn ORGEEV?

00:05:02.631 --> 00:05:06.810
nu, ORGEEV iz a kleyn shtetele. s'hobn gelebt dort a sakh yidn,

00:05:06.934 --> 00:05:08.649
shtark a sakh yidn.

00:05:08.824 --> 00:05:13.003
un dos lebn iz geven nit shlekht, bizkele Rusland iz gekumen.

00:05:13.195 --> 00:05:20.772
s'iz geven, ikh bin geven a kind, un ikh hob nit gevust gornisht. ikh hob gevust az ikh darf esn un trinken un geyn in shko- in shul arayn.

00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:25.777
un ven ikh bin geven a kind, bin ikh geven a, a tsienistke.

00:05:26.037 --> 00:05:28.258
ikh bin gegangen in Gordonye,

00:05:28.618 --> 00:05:31.362
un ikh hob gevolt forn keyn ISRAEL.

00:05:32.331 --> 00:05:32.918
'KAY.

00:05:32.918 --> 00:05:36.577
vos far a zakhn hostu geglaykht tsum shpiln?

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:40.559
ikh hob shtark ge- lib gehat tsu leyenen bikhlekh.

00:05:41.038 --> 00:05:42.871
dos iz geven mayn best.

00:05:42.945 --> 00:05:48.257
mayn muter fleg mir sh-, shikn in droys-, aroys in droysn shpiln, un ikh hob nisht gevolt, vayl

00:05:48.257 --> 00:05:49.706
ikh hob gevolt leyenen.

00:05:49.797 --> 00:05:51.546
kh'hob shtark lib gehat tsu leyenen.

00:05:51.602 --> 00:05:55.207
host geshpilt mit dayn shvester un bruder a sakh, tsu nisht?

00:05:53.863 --> 00:05:56.737
zey zenen geven elter fun mir,

00:05:56.737 --> 00:06:02.699
un ikh hob nisht gekont mit zey a sakh shpiln. kh'hob gehat nor a eltern bruder, vos er iz geshtorbn in der milkhome.

00:06:02.757 --> 00:06:07.948
er iz geven a bisl, yin-, yi-, azoy vi ikh, a bisl elter,

00:06:08.292 --> 00:06:10.007
nor mir flegn zikh shlogn.

00:06:11.346 --> 00:06:12.285
yo.

00:06:12.375 --> 00:06:15.389
zey hobn mikh lib gehat, derfar ikh bin geven di klenste.

00:06:15.919 --> 00:06:16.605
'KAY.

00:06:16.662 --> 00:06:21.195
vos kenstu undz dertseyln fun, yontoyvim in dayn hoym?

00:06:21.083 --> 00:06:24.266
 yo, mayne eltern hobn gegleybt in got,

00:06:24.272 --> 00:06:28.987
un zey hobn undz, ertsit az mir zoln gleybn in got oykhet.

00:06:29.098 --> 00:06:32.316
un mir hobn, ge-

00:06:32.322 --> 00:06:34.611
yontevet ile yontoyvim.

00:06:35.055 --> 00:06:40.685
ikh gedenk shtark gut, ven s'iz geven peysekh un ikh ho- fleg fregn di fir kashes,

00:06:40.708 --> 00:06:43.295
un ikh fleg zitsn in mitn,

00:06:43.295 --> 00:06:46.050
oyfn seyder, oyf kishn.

00:06:46.362 --> 00:06:49.177
ikh hob shtark lib gehat di yontoyvims un ikh,

00:06:49.177 --> 00:06:51.041
kh'hob shtark lib gehat yon-kiper.

00:06:51.041 --> 00:06:52.717
ikh fleg fastn,

00:06:52.774 --> 00:06:54.573
un fleg vayzn di tsung.

00:06:55.423 --> 00:07:00.513
host gehat a spetsyeln esn vos du host geglaykht fun d⟨en⟩ yontoyvim?

00:07:00.672 --> 00:07:01.678
yo.

00:07:01.887 --> 00:07:05.762
 peysekh hobn mir gehat, peysekhike latkes

00:07:05.970 --> 00:07:09.531
un, tsimesn un kezlekh.

00:07:09.531 --> 00:07:11.853
ikh hob shtark lib gehat fish.

00:07:12.383 --> 00:07:16.033
un bay undz oyf peysekh iz geven shtark a sakh mentshn.

00:07:16.033 --> 00:07:19.227
der p-, der foter mayner fleg, rufn;

00:07:19.227 --> 00:07:21.101
zey flegn esn bay undz,

00:07:21.411 --> 00:07:23.137
un s'iz geven freylekh.

00:07:23.082 --> 00:07:26.299
 vos far a mentshn hot gekumen tsu dayn hoyz?

00:07:26.001 --> 00:07:27.964
ma-, o-,

00:07:27.964 --> 00:07:30.231
mentshn vos zey hobn nisht gehat vos tsu esn

00:07:30.388 --> 00:07:33.841
flegn kumen tsun undz un mayn, mayn foter fleg zey gibn.

00:07:34.050 --> 00:07:38.364
un ikh hob lib gehat shtark oyftsuefenen di tir, Elyohu hanovi zol kumen.

00:07:39.772 --> 00:07:44.203
'KAY., hostu gehelft dayn mame a sakh ven du host geven a kind?

00:07:43.618 --> 00:07:47.560
neyn. ikh bin geven di klenste un mi- un ikh hob gornisht getun.

00:07:47.837 --> 00:07:49.214
mikh hot men

00:07:49.542 --> 00:07:50.751
bafrayt.

00:07:50.773 --> 00:07:56.504
mayn eltere shvester, zey, zi hot gefirt di shtub. zi fleg helfn der mame. di mame hot gearbet un der

00:07:56.528 --> 00:07:59.087
foter hot gearbet, un zi fleg undz helfn.

00:07:59.093 --> 00:08:00.876
un zi fleg mikh

00:08:01.354 --> 00:08:03.710
ontun un gibn esn.

00:08:04.088 --> 00:08:06.478
vos far a arbet hot dayn tate geton?

00:08:06.417 --> 00:08:08.368
mayn tate hot gehat kleytn.

00:08:08.627 --> 00:08:11.371
er hot gehat a sakh melokhes un veynik brokhes.

00:08:12.323 --> 00:08:15.540
er hot gehat kleytn un er hot gehat, mir hobn gehat a,

00:08:15.867 --> 00:08:18.595
a F- a F- a FACTORY fun,

00:08:18.820 --> 00:08:21.902
 vaser. gemakht, sode-vaser.

00:08:22.650 --> 00:08:24.804
 marozhene, ICE CREAM.

00:08:27.055 --> 00:08:30.474
un ikh veys az kh'bin geven, nit shlekht, in der heym.

00:08:29.923 --> 00:08:33.747
s'iz geven dayn tate's a FACTORY, oder an ander man's?

00:08:32.455 --> 00:08:35.894
mayn tate's. mayn tate's, m- in eynem mit di brider,

00:08:35.894 --> 00:08:38.197
hobn zey gearbet. zey hobn gearbet shver,

00:08:38.197 --> 00:08:39.958
nor ikh hob gornisht gefilt.

00:08:40.167 --> 00:08:41.443
ikh bin geven...

00:08:40.319 --> 00:08:41.319
UNK

00:08:41.414 --> 00:08:44.885
un du zogst az dayn mame hot gearbet. vos hot zi gearbet?

00:08:43.980 --> 00:08:45.864
in eynem mit mayn foter.

00:08:45.853 --> 00:08:47.281
in di zelbe plats?

00:08:46.275 --> 00:08:48.178
zi iz geshtanen in kleyt,

00:08:48.178 --> 00:08:51.942
un ile kinder hobn geholfn, di eltere. ikh hob nokh nisht.

00:08:51.942 --> 00:08:53.070
ikh bin geven nokh

00:08:53.211 --> 00:08:54.203
tsu yung,

00:08:54.203 --> 00:08:55.247
tsu kleyn.

00:08:55.287 --> 00:09:00.428
hot andere mentshn geleb⟨n⟩ in dayn zelbe hoyz mit, mit dayne f- familye?

00:08:59.404 --> 00:09:02.587
neyn, mir ⟨ho'mir⟩, mir hobn gelebt a- al- aleyn.

00:09:03.201 --> 00:09:04.916
mir hobn gelebt bazunder.

00:09:05.530 --> 00:09:06.176
'KAY.

00:09:07.619 --> 00:09:13.542
ven du host geven kleyn, hostu, geganen tsu a,

00:09:13.542 --> 00:09:17.066
kh'veys nisht vi tsu zogn in yidish, tsu A GROUP OR A CAMP,

00:09:17.241 --> 00:09:19.091
A YOUTH ORGANIZATION?

00:09:19.671 --> 00:09:23.681
 ikh hob gezogt az ikh bin gegan, geven a tsienistke; ikh bin gegan in Gordonye.

00:09:22.185 --> 00:09:23.191
UNK.

00:09:24.160 --> 00:09:29.048
un, in zumer flegn mir f- avekforn in, a dorf

00:09:29.408 --> 00:09:30.499
tomed.

00:09:30.758 --> 00:09:33.502
kh'bin geven, bay undz hot men gezogt oyf a datshe.

00:09:33.660 --> 00:09:34.346
⟨o⟩.

