dos hob ikh gehert.

00:09:36.478 --> 00:09:37.467
ya.

00:09:40.562 --> 00:09:43.782
in, in dayn berg, in ORGEEV,

00:09:43.782 --> 00:09:46.817
hot geven mentshn vos zaynen nisht yidishe?

00:09:46.975 --> 00:09:47.849
 yo!

00:09:47.849 --> 00:09:49.601
avade s'iz geven mentshn

00:09:49.641 --> 00:09:52.132
vos zenen geven, rumenishe,

00:09:52.527 --> 00:09:55.794
un s'iz geven a sakh rusishe mentshn.

00:09:56.155 --> 00:09:57.938
s'iz geven ⟨i⟩lerley mentshn.

00:09:58.213 --> 00:09:59.610
 vi hobn zey

00:09:59.610 --> 00:10:01.734
gekumen tsuzamen mit di yidn?

00:10:02.179 --> 00:10:06.116
POCHTI, zey, zey ⟨un⟩ mir, mir flegn zikh nit azoy a sakh bagegenen,

00:10:06.116 --> 00:10:08.417
nor ikh hob gehat a sakh FRIENDS,

00:10:08.592 --> 00:10:11.927
 rumenishe FRIENDS. mir hobn gelernt in shkole.

00:10:11.983 --> 00:10:15.031
mir flegn zikh bagegenen. nor kh'hob gevust az ikh bin a yid.

00:10:15.882 --> 00:10:18.103
kh'hob demlt gevust shoyn az ikh bin a yid.

00:10:18.177 --> 00:10:19.903
hobn zey ir,

00:10:19.903 --> 00:10:24.321
 getshepet o- oder ge- ⟨⟩...?

00:10:24.100 --> 00:10:28.999
 neyn., far der milkhome iz shoyn geven erger, derfar vos,

00:10:28.999 --> 00:10:31.467
s'iz geven a PARTY KUZISTY.

00:10:31.744 --> 00:10:34.366
