00:10:41.734 --> 00:10:42.386
in...

00:10:43.810 --> 00:10:46.031
in velkhe yorn hot dos geven?

00:10:45.615 --> 00:10:49.996
s'iz geven in di fertsikste yorn, ey- eyder s'iz gekumen tsu, Rusland tsun undz.

00:10:50.728 --> 00:10:51.316
'KAY.

00:10:51.316 --> 00:10:53.020
hostu gehert fun,

00:10:53.020 --> 00:10:56.375
 di onfang fu⟨l⟩ milkhome in ander platsn?

00:10:57.293 --> 00:10:58.637
farsht⟨UNK⟩ ⟨nit⟩ vos...

00:10:58.356 --> 00:11:01.070
hostu gehert fun di

