onfangen f- fun di milkhome in a- in ander sht- sh⟨UNK⟩?

00:11:03.385 --> 00:11:07.128
yo, kh'hob gehert, m⟨e-⟩ a sakh gehert. ikh bin geven,

00:11:07.128 --> 00:11:09.752
ikh hob gezogt az ikh hob shtark lib gehat tsu lernen,

00:11:09.752 --> 00:11:13.588
un kh'hob lib gehat tsu leyenen. ikh hob geleyenen -leyent di NEWSPAPERS,

00:11:13.611 --> 00:11:15.388
un ikh hob gehert vegn GITLERn,

00:11:15.388 --> 00:11:17.722
un kh'hob, mir hobn shtark moyre gehat far GITLERn.

00:11:17.982 --> 00:11:21.384
mir hobn nisht moyre gehat far der milkhome, nor mir hobn moyre gehat far GITLERn.

00:11:21.694 --> 00:11:24.286
mir hobn gevust az GITLER harget yidn.

00:11:24.681 --> 00:11:27.065
mir hobn gehert vos s'iz geven in PoylAND.

00:11:27.065 --> 00:11:30.226
mir hobn gehert vos s'iz geven in, in GERMANY.

00:11:30.604 --> 00:11:33.444
un mir hobn gevust az s'vet zayn shtark shlekht far undz

00:11:33.444 --> 00:11:36.031
az GITLER vet kumen tsun undz.

00:11:36.409 --> 00:11:38.574
mir hobn moyre gehat; mayn foter iz geven shtark a,

00:11:38.574 --> 00:11:39.930
a kluger mentsh,

00:11:39.970 --> 00:11:42.158
un er fleg undz zogn di gantse tsayt.

00:11:43.648 --> 00:11:47.559
un v- vos far a zakhn hot er ge- ⟨⟩,

00:11:47.559 --> 00:11:49.391
geredn fun in der heym,

00:11:49.391 --> 00:11:52.073
vos tsu ton, ⟨⟩...?

00:11:51.799 --> 00:11:54.307
nu, mir hobn shtark gegleybt in Rusland,

00:11:54.617 --> 00:11:58.495
un mir hobn, gemeynt az Rusland... un s'iz take azoy geven...

00:11:58.495 --> 00:12:00.807
vet undz bafrayen fun GITLERn.

00:12:01.030 --> 00:12:02.829
mir hobn gegleybt in Rusland.

00:12:02.953 --> 00:12:04.820
mir hobn gegleybt in komunizm.

00:12:05.603 --> 00:12:08.162
mir hobn nit gevust vos s'iz, nor mir hobn gegleybt.

00:12:11.113 --> 00:12:13.291
,

00:12:13.618 --> 00:12:14.776
dayn

00:12:15.593 --> 00:12:17.207
bruder un shvester

00:12:17.432 --> 00:12:20.137
hobn gearbet di gantse ⟨ta-⟩ dayn shvester,

00:12:20.137 --> 00:12:21.560
in di heym, ⟨⟩?

00:12:20.166 --> 00:12:26.302
mayn, mayn shvester iz geven in der heym, un mayn bruder, mayn bruder, ven zey hobn gekontshet tsu lernen,

00:12:26.359 --> 00:12:28.648
hobn zey geholfn mayn foter.

00:12:29.548 --> 00:12:32.140
may- ⟨, un⟩ mayn shvester

00:12:32.316 --> 00:12:35.735
hot, ⟨ho-⟩ gelernt, un zi iz geven a tsienistke,

00:12:35.978 --> 00:12:39.144
un, zi iz gegangen in Gordonye,

00:12:39.201 --> 00:12:41.473
un ven zi iz geven alt zekhtsn yor

00:12:41.631 --> 00:12:44.713
iz zi avekgeforn makhn di HAKHSHARA.

00:12:44.871 --> 00:12:46.569
azoy zogt men oyf HAKHSHARA?

00:12:46.812 --> 00:12:50.378
 un m'hot zi GOTOV⟨e-⟩ me, m'hot zi

00:12:50.378 --> 00:12:52.712
tsugegreyt tsu forn keyn IZRAIL'.

00:12:52.920 --> 00:12:57.774
un zi hot shtark gevolt forn in IZRAIL'. s'iz geven dos, ⟨in⟩ fertsikstn yor.

00:12:58.067 --> 00:13:01.233
un s'hobn, ku- s'zenen gekumen Rusland,

00:13:02.117 --> 00:13:03.849
hot zi shoyn nisht gekont forn.

00:13:04.446 --> 00:13:07.392
vos hostu getrakht, ven du host geven a kind,

00:13:07.392 --> 00:13:09.367
az du vest ton ven,

00:13:09.373 --> 00:13:11.223
⟨⟩, du verst elter?

00:13:10.993 --> 00:13:13.133
ikh hob shtark gevolt, gevolt

00:13:13.133 --> 00:13:14.514
zayn a dokter.

00:13:15.432 --> 00:13:18.137
hostu gevisn andere mentshn, andere

00:13:18.137 --> 00:13:21.164
 meydlekh v- vos hobn geven doktern?

00:13:20.224 --> 00:13:24.571
yo. ikh hob gev- gezen az a dokter helft mentshn

00:13:24.612 --> 00:13:26.800
un ikh hob oykhet gevolt helfn mentshn.

00:13:28.746 --> 00:13:31.676
vos hot dayn mame un tate gedenkt fun dos?

00:13:32.678 --> 00:13:36.671
nu, mayn mame un tate... bay undz iz geven azoy, az a meydl

00:13:36.913 --> 00:13:38.375
darf nisht lernen.

00:13:38.449 --> 00:13:40.957
a meydl vert elter un hot khasene.

00:13:41.976 --> 00:13:47.189
ot dos hot getrakht mayn ta- mayn tate, nor ven s'iz gekumen Rusland, hot er shoyn azoy nisht getrakht.

00:13:48.338 --> 00:13:48.889
'KAY.

00:13:50.633 --> 00:13:52.871
ven gedenkstu az

00:13:53.063 --> 00:13:55.253
du host gevisn tsu ersht

00:13:55.253 --> 00:13:56.617
fun di milkhome?

00:13:57.012 --> 00:13:59.756
dem ershtn tog hob ikh shoyn gevust fun der milkhome.

00:13:59.408 --> 00:14:01.191
ven hot dos geven?

00:13:59.998 --> 00:14:04.582
s'iz geven in, eyn un tsvontsikstn, tsvey un tsvontsikstn IUN',

00:14:04.926 --> 00:14:08.818
un m'hot ongehoybn tsu varfn bombes in Kiv,

00:14:09.111 --> 00:14:12.246
un s'iz nisht vayt fun ⟨undze-⟩ fun undz geven Kiv.

00:14:12.246 --> 00:14:14.336
un arum tsen a zeyger

00:14:14.427 --> 00:14:18.556
hot geredt,... mir hobn nokh nisht gehat keyn, radyo;

00:14:18.556 --> 00:14:22.453
mir hobn gehat a, a UNK ⟨a min⟩ ⟨totshke⟩, ⟨kh'veys vi s'heyst⟩...

00:14:22.493 --> 00:14:26.655
un, Molotov hot geredt az s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome,

00:14:26.847 --> 00:14:31.988
un mayn, m- mayn muter hot ongehoybn shtark veynen, derfar zi hot moyre gehat far di zinen.

00:14:32.854 --> 00:14:36.493
un in fakt, dem andern tog hot men avekgenemen mayn bruder,

00:14:36.837 --> 00:14:38.366
mayn eltster bruder.

00:14:37.933 --> 00:14:40.272
hostu gevisn vu zey zaynen im

00:14:40.110 --> 00:14:44.132
hot im avekgenemen in der milkhome, un mir hobn shtark geveynt un

00:14:40.380 --> 00:14:41.572
avek⟨genumen⟩?

00:14:44.132 --> 00:14:47.816
mayn muter hot shtark geveynt, un UNK, un er hot ir gezogt,

00:14:49.189 --> 00:14:50.769
"mame, vos veynstu?

00:14:51.484 --> 00:14:52.710
ikh gey,

00:14:53.509 --> 00:14:55.295
ikh gey far,

00:14:55.973 --> 00:14:57.148
far undz.

00:14:57.627 --> 00:15:00.020
mir darfn derhargenen fashistn,

00:15:00.327 --> 00:15:02.751
derfar vos s'iz gut far undz, far yidn.

00:15:02.740 --> 00:15:03.628
⟨er v-⟩...

00:15:02.757 --> 00:15:04.067
darfst nisht veynen."

00:15:05.052 --> 00:15:07.172
vemen hot im avekgenemen?

00:15:06.722 --> 00:15:09.095
dem andern tog. s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome

00:15:09.152 --> 00:15:14.124
dem tsvey un tsvontsikstn, un efsher dem dray un tsvontsikstn tsi dem fir un tsvontsikstn ⟨hot men im⟩ avekgenemen.

00:15:14.535 --> 00:15:19.119
vemen hot im g- avekgenemen? ver hot gekumt tsu dayn hoyz oder...?

00:15:18.602 --> 00:15:22.345
NO, m'hot im geshikt a, a ⟨NOTICE⟩

00:15:22.345 --> 00:15:24.418
un m'hot im gesh- avekgenemen.

00:15:24.778 --> 00:15:28.366
un er iz avekgegangen, un mir hobn im ⟨ge-⟩ zenen gegangen im,

00:15:24.812 --> 00:15:25.734
tsu...

00:15:28.373 --> 00:15:33.744
bizkele, etlekhe kilometer⟨n⟩, zenen mir gegangen im, mit im,

00:15:33.807 --> 00:15:35.758
un er iz gegangen mit der armey.

00:15:36.827 --> 00:15:38.272
mit di rusish⟨e⟩?

00:15:37.097 --> 00:15:40.770
un mir hobn shta-... mit der rusisher armey... mir hobn shtark geveynt un...

00:15:40.860 --> 00:15:43.841
hostu gevisn vu zey shikn im, tsu nisht?

00:15:43.037 --> 00:15:47.622
ikh hob gevust, UNK, ikh hob gevust aldings; ikh bin shoyn geven tsvelef yor alt.

00:15:47.622 --> 00:15:50.561
ikh hob gevust, un ikh hob moyre gehat shtark.

00:15:50.715 --> 00:15:52.683
ikh hob shtark moyre gehat

00:15:52.977 --> 00:15:57.510
az s'vet vern, s'vet zayn shtark paskudne, mir'n nisht hobn vos tsu esn.

00:15:57.583 --> 00:16:00.457
un ikh hob shtark, faynt gehat tsu esn,

00:16:00.457 --> 00:16:02.162
 smetene.

00:16:02.162 --> 00:16:03.394
hob ikh gezogt mayn mame,

00:16:03.394 --> 00:16:04.243
",

00:16:04.401 --> 00:16:09.305
zay nisht, darfst zikh nisht, ba- baruik; ikh'l shoyn esn smetene."

00:16:10.729 --> 00:16:12.714
yo, dos iz geven azoy oykh.

00:16:13.949 --> 00:16:17.186
hobn a sakh soldatn gekumen tsu ORGEEV?

00:16:17.209 --> 00:16:18.249
yo.

00:16:18.475 --> 00:16:23.475
s'iz geven nisht vayt fun der grenets un di, azoy vi ir veyst, di daytshn

00:16:23.475 --> 00:16:27.044
hobn tsugenemen a sakh PLACES di ershte teg

00:16:27.044 --> 00:16:30.264
fun der milkhome, iz shoyn geven tsugenemen a sakh PLACES.

00:16:30.321 --> 00:16:33.032
un mir ⟨z- hobn⟩ gevoynt nisht vayt fun der grenets,

00:16:33.207 --> 00:16:35.344
 un s'iz geven shtark a sakh soldatn.

00:16:35.772 --> 00:16:39.647
un mir hobn gezen, azoy zey geyen avek, un s'iz geven a geferlekhe

00:16:40.007 --> 00:16:41.317
pan- PANIC.

00:16:41.998 --> 00:16:44.844
un s'iz geven, shreklekh iz geven.

00:16:45.171 --> 00:16:46.898
un vo- vos hot

00:16:45.188 --> 00:16:46.571
geven shreklekh.

00:16:46.898 --> 00:16:49.449
dayn familye geton, dayn pa-...?

00:16:48.192 --> 00:16:50.146
mayn familye,

00:16:50.146 --> 00:16:54.243
shpeter mit etlekhe teg fun der milkhome, s'iz geven in IYUL',

00:16:54.300 --> 00:16:55.441
JULY,

00:16:56.342 --> 00:17:01.095
iz mayn foter hot, gehat a f- a ferd

00:17:01.388 --> 00:17:03.072
mit a vegele.

00:17:03.072 --> 00:17:06.141
hobn mir zikh oyfgezetst ile oyfn f- oyfn vegele.

00:17:06.231 --> 00:17:09.476
mayn b-, bruder, der mitlster bruder,

00:17:09.476 --> 00:17:12.332
iz geven, er iz geven a UCHITEL',

00:17:12.660 --> 00:17:13.869
a TEACHER,

00:17:14.297 --> 00:17:19.134
a lerer. er, iz er gegangen, hot men im genemen arbetn zumer.

00:17:19.967 --> 00:17:21.733
iz er nisht geven mit undz.

00:17:22.161 --> 00:17:25.597
nor ikh mit mayn, bruder, der klenster,

00:17:25.738 --> 00:17:29.245
un mayne shvester, mayn foter un mayn muter

00:17:29.245 --> 00:17:32.043
hobn zikh oyfgezetst oyf a f-, a,

00:17:32.438 --> 00:17:34.856
a vegl, mit a, mit a ferd,

00:17:34.856 --> 00:17:37.241
un mir zenen geforn. vuhin hobn mir nit gevust.

00:17:37.500 --> 00:17:40.869
mir zenen geforn, ⟨iz⟩ geven a s⟨h⟩akh mentshn. s'iz geven geferlekh.

00:17:41.145 --> 00:17:43.091
geven a groyser panik.

00:17:43.373 --> 00:17:46.826
un mir zenen avekgegangen, mir hobn nisht gevust, mir zenen gegangen tsu dem Nester.

00:17:47.220 --> 00:17:50.136
 nisht vayt fun undz iz geven der Nester.

00:17:50.136 --> 00:17:51.174
der Nester

00:17:51.174 --> 00:17:55.584
hot ge- iz geven nokh Rusland. mir zenen geven in Moldavye,

00:17:55.607 --> 00:17:59.974
un der Nester iz geven, hot UNK iz, iz geven a taykh

00:17:59.974 --> 00:18:02.122
vos me geyt keyn Rusland.

00:18:02.122 --> 00:18:04.460
hobn mir gedarft durkhgeyn dem taykh.

00:18:05.023 --> 00:18:07.109
un s'iz geven a geferlekhe panik.

00:18:08.398 --> 00:18:09.860
un oyfn veg,

00:18:09.917 --> 00:18:14.298
ven mir zenen geforn, hot zikh ibergekert dos vegl, vegele,

00:18:14.355 --> 00:18:15.851
un ikh bin gefaln,

00:18:16.161 --> 00:18:21.977
un, kh'hob gekhapt a, a, a klap in oyg... ikh hob nokh a simen itster oykh...

00:18:22.354 --> 00:18:24.137
un s'hot ongehoybn geyn blut.

00:18:24.784 --> 00:18:29.013
un derfar vos ikh aleyn bin geven oyf dem vegele... ile zenen gegan tsu fus,

00:18:29.290 --> 00:18:32.136
nor ikh bin geven di klenste, hot men mikh avekgezetst...

00:18:32.344 --> 00:18:36.151
un, hob ikh mikh shtark dershrokn. un s'iz gegangen ⟨in⟩ blut,

00:18:36.310 --> 00:18:39.707
un keyn vaser iz nisht geven, keyn doktoyrim iz nisht geven,

00:18:39.707 --> 00:18:41.856
un mayn muter hot ongehoybn veynen.

00:18:42.165 --> 00:18:46.411
iz, hot zi ge- avekgeshikt mikh mit der elterer shvester,

00:18:46.452 --> 00:18:49.298
 tsun a dokter, zukhn a dokter.

00:18:49.776 --> 00:18:53.653
 un zenen mir gegangen, un mir hobn gefunen a dokter, un er hot mi⟨kh⟩ a bisl,

00:18:53.653 --> 00:18:57.802
 opgevashn dos oyg un gegibn a bisl TREATMENT.

00:18:58.568 --> 00:19:04.974
un dernokh dem ⟨ho-⟩ zenen mir gegangen, mir hobn gezukht, d- dernokh dem mayne eltern, ven mir hobn zikh umgekert,

00:19:05.048 --> 00:19:08.349
hot ongehoybn shtark tsu, varfn bombes,

00:19:08.490 --> 00:19:11.808
un mentshn hobn zikh, farbahaltn in, in groz,

00:19:12.017 --> 00:19:15.740
un mir hobn nisht gevust vu tsu geyn. s'iz geven shtark a sakh mentshn.

00:19:15.983 --> 00:19:21.377
un mir hobn nisht gevust vu tsu geyn, un mir hobn farloyrn di eltern. ikh mit mayn shvester hobn farloyrn di eltern.

00:19:21.214 --> 00:19:24.768
un di klenste bruder hot geven nokh mit di...?

00:19:23.070 --> 00:19:28.093
un der klenster bruder iz geven mit di, mit di, mi-, nor ikh mit mayn shvester,

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:26.895
di eltern.

00:19:28.183 --> 00:19:34.994
mayn, der eltster shvester, un mayne eltern mit dem, klenstn bruder un mit der shvester, vos iz itster in IZRAIL',

00:19:35.153 --> 00:19:37.918
iz geblibn, un mir zenen gegangen zukhn a dokter.

00:19:37.918 --> 00:19:41.593
un mir zenen aheymgekumen... krikgegangen, nisht aheymgekumen, krikgegangen...

00:19:41.683 --> 00:19:44.883
hobn mir shoyn keynem nisht gefunen. mir hobn nisht gevust vu zey zenen.

00:19:44.907 --> 00:19:47.736
mentshn zenen gelign oyf der erd, toyt.

00:19:47.877 --> 00:19:55.161
un s'iz, geven, s'hot zikh gevalgert, o- ontuekhts mit, mi- vo- m- vos ir vilt iz geven oyf der erd.

00:19:55.538 --> 00:19:59.188
un mir hobn nit gevust vu tsu geyn, zenen mir gegangen mit ile mentshn tsu dem,

00:19:59.188 --> 00:20:00.999
 RIVER Dnester.

00:20:01.798 --> 00:20:03.969
un bay dem RIVER Dnester

00:20:03.975 --> 00:20:06.030
hot zikh getrofn,

00:20:06.030 --> 00:20:08.137
shtark sh- geferlekhe zakhn.

00:20:08.329 --> 00:20:11.816
 mentshn zenen der-, dertrunken gevorn

00:20:11.890 --> 00:20:13.268
oyf ⟨briks⟩.

00:20:13.780 --> 00:20:16.170
un do iz ge- gefaln bombes.

00:20:16.632 --> 00:20:21.334
un mir zenen gegangen, gegangen. mir hobn gezukht di eltern, un di eltern hobn mir nisht gekent gefinen,

00:20:21.947 --> 00:20:25.521
bizkele mir zenen ongekumen in a, in a shtetl,

00:20:25.521 --> 00:20:27.324
iz do a shtetl ⟨ATAKA⟩,

00:20:27.803 --> 00:20:30.936
un s'iz nisht vay- nisht vayt fun MOGILЁV-Podolsk.

00:20:31.228 --> 00:20:36.136
zenen mir, nokh dem gegangen keyn MOGILЁV-Podolsk, un ikh hob gemuzt hobn a dokter,

00:20:36.136 --> 00:20:38.698
derfar vos s'hot mir shtark vey geton dos oyg.

00:20:39.160 --> 00:20:42.768
un dort hobn mir gefunen a sakh yidn; in MOGILЁV-Podolsk

00:20:42.768 --> 00:20:44.485
hobn gelebt a sakh yidn.

00:20:44.863 --> 00:20:48.856
hobn mir, un es iz oykhet geven dort a panike. mentshn hobn moyre gehat.

00:20:48.964 --> 00:20:51.033
iz, a,

00:20:51.630 --> 00:20:55.609
a familye hot m- hot undz genemen un m'hot mikh gefirt tsun a dokter.

00:20:55.609 --> 00:20:58.377
in Rusland iz geven, doktoyrim on gelt.

00:20:58.377 --> 00:21:00.045
s'iz nokh geven dort Rusland.

00:21:00.270 --> 00:21:03.085
hot ⟨men⟩ mir nokh a mol gemakht a PRIVYAZKe, a,

00:21:03.085 --> 00:21:04.179
a BANDAGE,

00:21:04.354 --> 00:21:06.958
un, un zey hobn undz gezogt,

00:21:06.958 --> 00:21:08.347
"vu vet ir geyn?

00:21:08.826 --> 00:21:13.443
vu vet zi geyn? zitst mit undz. vos vet zayn mit undz, vet zayn mit aykh, mit, mit ir oykh."

00:21:13.467 --> 00:21:16.484
"mir viln, mir viln geyn tsu di eltern."

00:21:16.484 --> 00:21:18.657
"ken zayn az di eltern zenen shoyn nishto.

00:21:18.867 --> 00:21:20.112
vu vet ir geyn?"

00:21:19.879 --> 00:21:21.020
ven hot...

00:21:20.112 --> 00:21:22.185
shtark voyle mentshn geven.

00:21:21.904 --> 00:21:23.619
ven hot dos geven?

00:21:23.187 --> 00:21:25.982
s'iz geven, dos in IYUL',

00:21:25.988 --> 00:21:27.096
JULY,

00:21:27.405 --> 00:21:28.985
MAYBE IN JULY.

00:21:27.658 --> 00:21:29.069
in velkhe yor?

00:21:29.127 --> 00:21:30.877
in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:21:29.464 --> 00:21:30.572
⟨un⟩ fertsik.

00:21:30.696 --> 00:21:31.511
un,

00:21:30.877 --> 00:21:32.428
in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:21:31.511 --> 00:21:34.689
 gedenkstu di familye's nomen?

00:21:33.970 --> 00:21:36.810
yo, ikh gedenk es, tomed vel ikh es gedenken.

00:21:36.810 --> 00:21:38.486
di familye iz geven ⟨KOPYT⟩.

00:21:40.180 --> 00:21:44.376
un zey hobn undz genemen tsu zikh, un der foter hot gebakn broyt.

00:21:45.377 --> 00:21:49.997
un mir hobn dort gearbet. vos mir hobn gekont, hobn mir hel- geholfn. ikh bin geven no⟨kh⟩ a kind,

00:21:49.997 --> 00:21:52.163
nor mayn shvester hot gekont merert.

00:21:52.633 --> 00:21:56.609
nor mir hobn gemeynt az mir'n ibervartn dort di milkhome, nor...

00:21:57.392 --> 00:22:01.048
 shpeter mit a khoydesh... ikh gedenk nisht vifl TOCHNO,

00:22:01.223 --> 00:22:02.941
pinktlekh gedenk ikh nisht...

00:22:02.941 --> 00:22:05.622
zenen gekumen di gute NEMTSn,

00:22:05.622 --> 00:22:07.016
di gute,

00:22:07.016 --> 00:22:08.197
GERMANS,

00:22:08.197 --> 00:22:10.161
un hobn farkhapt ot dos shtetl.

00:22:10.690 --> 00:22:16.539
un, nor s'iz geven, dos ershte zenen gekumen ahin tsu rumenishe SOLDIERn. mir hobn gekont shtark gut rumenish.

00:22:16.765 --> 00:22:18.564
hobn mir ongehoybn redn mit zey.

00:22:19.127 --> 00:22:20.960
un mir hobn,

00:22:21.135 --> 00:22:24.099
a bisl gevoynt, bay zey in shtub.

00:22:24.156 --> 00:22:26.647
un efsher iz geven dos in ⟨de⟩tsember,

00:22:27.582 --> 00:22:29.618
hot men undz avekgenemen in geto.

00:22:30.754 --> 00:22:32.216
un dort iz shoyn geven,

